Tyrael: And for me too. I will ty to convince Blackheart that you are 
not the threat right now, but I doubt it will give any results. 
Farewell!

He soars into the sky and opens a channel with the newly arrived 
Tripredacus ship.

Tyrael: Blackheart, this is Tyrael. The battle is over and I am 
heading your way. Before you do anything, wait for my debriefing.
